ni.png?m=1659331259", "stars": 8049, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 358047, "username": "x97bgt", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/x97bgt", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/470d45256ee34438b017cfb002857fef?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/470d45256ee34438b017cfb002857fef?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/470d45256ee34438b017cfb002857fef?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1540298253, "last_modified": 1643619614}, "last_reply_by": "janus77", "last_touched": 1667119075, "title": "突然发现自己一直以错误的方式打字", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/891131", "created": 1667106806, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://cdn.sspai.com/2018/07/28/2af01b986a097e3f16a2e9a9ff0b3562.png?imageView2/2/w/1120/q/90/interlace/1/ignore-error/1)\r\n\r\n今天看了这张图后，观察了自己打字的模式，发现我自己无意识地想用食指控制大部分范围，比如用左手食指打 C ，右手食指打 B 和，（逗号）等。然后也会无意识地不想使用无名指。这样导致手在键盘上会经常左右移动，无形中降低了效率。\r\n\r\n大家会有这样的情况吗", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.sspai.com/2018/07/28/2af01b986a097e3f16a2e9a9ff0b3562.png?imageView2/2/w/1120/q/90/interlace/1/ignore-error/1\"/></p>\n<p>今天看了这张图后，观察了自己打字的模式，发现我自己无意识地想用食指控制大部分范围，比如用左手食指打 C ，右手食指打 B 和，（逗号）等。然后也会无意识地不想使用无名指。这样导致手在键盘上会经常左右移动，无形中降低了效率。</p>\n<p>大家会有这样的情况吗</p>\n", "last_modified": 1667106869, "replies": 38, "id": 891131}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 9810, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar